<h3 class="section_title">Act I</h3>
<div id="section_77245" class="section">
<h3 class="section_title">SCENE I. A desert place.</h3>
<div class="text">
<blockquote>
<p><em>Thunder and lightning. Enter three Witches</em></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>First Witch</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>When shall we three meet again<br />
In thunder, lightning, or in rain?<br /></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Second Witch</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>When the hurlyburly's done,<br />
When the battle's lost and won.<br /></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Third Witch</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>That will be ere the set of sun.<br /></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>First Witch</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Where the place?<br /></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Second Witch</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Upon the heath.<br /></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Third Witch</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>There to meet with Macbeth.<br /></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>First Witch</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>I come, Graymalkin!<br /></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Second Witch</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Paddock calls.<br /></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>Third Witch</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Anon.<br /></p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>ALL</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p>Fair is foul, and foul is fair:<br />
Hover through the fog and filthy air.<br /></p>
<p><em>Exeunt</em></p>
</blockquote>
<p>&#160;</p>
